high_descs: Move over to your right where the tennis racket is leaning up against the desk.
Pick up the tennis racket from the floor.
Turn left, walk forward a few steps, then turn left again to face the nightstand.
Turn on the lamp that is on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket under the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Move to your right so that you are standing in front of the end of the of the desk to your right.
Pick up the tennis racket, on the floor, leaning against the end of the desk.
Turn around and go to the night stand to your left, to the right of the door.
Turn on the lamp in the back right corner on the night stand, to the right of the door.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp on the night stand.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the room on the floor by the desk where the racket is
Pick up the racket sitting on the floor
Carry the racket to the opposite side of the room where the nightstand is with the lamp
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Carry a racket while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Turn right, move towards the mirror on the wall, then turn left and move towards the edge of the desk.
Pick up the tennis racket on the floor next to the desk.
Turn left and move towards the small cabinet to the right of the door.
Turn on the lamp that is on top of the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket using the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and take a step so you are facing the desk length wise.
Pick up the tennis racquet leaning on the side of the dresser.
Turn left and position yourself in front of the small stand to your left that has a light on it and face it.
Turn the light on.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a light after picking up a tennis racquet.

high_descs: Turn right towards the tennis racket on the floor.
Pick up the racket from the floor.
Turn left, walk towards the edge of the bed, turn left towards the desk with the lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket by the light of a green lamp.
